sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户 Shift+Tab
    participant Cycle as cyclePermissionMode()<br/>副作用协调层
    participant Pure as getNextPermissionMode()<br/>纯计算层
    participant Gate as canCycleToAuto()<br/>双重检查门禁
    participant Apply as transitionPermissionMode()<br/>副作用执行层

    User->>Cycle: 触发切换
    Cycle->>Pure: 计算下一模式（纯函数）
    Pure->>Gate: 可以进入 auto？
    Gate-->>Pure: 缓存值 AND 实时值
    Pure-->>Cycle: nextMode: PermissionMode
    Cycle->>Apply: 应用新状态（有副作用）
    Apply-->>Cycle: 更新后的 context
    Cycle-->>User: { nextMode, context }
